{{Infobox language |name=Kato |nativename=Cahto |region=[[California]] ([[Eel River (California)|Eel River]]) |ethnicity=[[Cahto people]] |extinct=1960s |ref=e18 |familycolor=Dené-Yeniseian |fam2=[[Na-Dené languages|Na-Dené]] |fam3=[[Athabaskan languages|Athabaskan]] |fam4=[[Pacific Coast Athabaskan languages|Pacific Coast Athabaskan]] |fam5=California Athabaskan |iso3=ktw |glotto=kato1244 |glottorefname=Kato }}
'''Cahto''' (also spelled '''Kato''') is an [[language death|extinct]] [[Athabaskan languages|Athabaskan]] language that was formerly spoken by the [[Kato (tribe)|Kato people]] of the Laytonville and Branscomb area at the head of the [[South Fork Eel River|South Fork of the Eel River]]. It is one of the four languages belonging to the ''California Athabaskan'' cluster of the [[Pacific Coast Athabaskan languages]]. Most Kato speakers were bilingual in [[Northern Pomo]] and some also spoke [[Yuki language|Yuki]]. ==Phonology== ===Consonants=== {| class="wikitable" style=text-align:center |-style="font-size: 90%;" !colspan=1 rowspan=1| !colspan=1 rowspan=1| [[Labial consonant|Labial]] !colspan=3 rowspan=1| [[Dental consonant|Dental]] ! rowspan="1" | [[Alveolar consonant|Alveolar]] !colspan=3 rowspan=1| [[Postalveolar consonant|Post-alveolar]] !colspan=3 rowspan=1| [[Palatal consonant|Palatal]] !colspan=3 rowspan=1| [[Velar consonant|Velar]] !colspan=1 rowspan=1| [[Uvular consonant|Uvular]] !colspan=1 rowspan=1| [[Glottal consonant|Glottal]] |- !colspan=1 rowspan=1|[[Nasal consonant|Nasal]] |colspan=1|{{IPAblink|m}} '''m''' |colspan=3| |{{IPAblink|n}} '''n''' |colspan=3| |colspan=3| |colspan=3|{{IPAblink|ŋ}} '''ñ''' |colspan=1| |colspan=1| |- !colspan=1 rowspan=2|[[Stop consonant|Stop]] |colspan=1 rowspan=2|{{IPAblink|b}} '''b''' |colspan=1 rowspan=2 style="border-right: 0;|{{IPAblink|tʰ}} '''t'''||colspan=1 rowspan=2 style="border-right: 0; border-left: 0;"|{{IPAblink|tʼ}} '''t''''||colspan=1 rowspan=2 style="border-left: 0;"|{{IPAblink|d}} '''d''' | rowspan="2" |{{IPAblink|ts}} '''ts''' {{IPAblink|tsʼ}} '''ts'''' |colspan=3 rowspan=2| |colspan=3 rowspan=1 style="border-bottom: 0;"|<small>Before front vowel</small> |colspan=3 rowspan=1 style="border-bottom: 0;"|<small>Before back vowel</small> |colspan=1 rowspan=2|{{IPAblink|k}}~{{IPAblink|q}} '''q''' |colspan=1 rowspan=2|{{IPAblink|ʔ}} '''′''' |- |colspan=1 rowspan=1 style="border-right: 0; border-top: 0;"|{{IPAblink|